    <title>Linux好用命令之crontab</title>
    <link href="https://www.dddachui.top/posts/9191c4a8.html"/>
    <id>https://www.dddachui.top/posts/9191c4a8.html</id>
    <published>2022-04-02T16:00:00.000Z</published>
    <updated>2023-03-13T04:52:13.373Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="命令简介"><a href="#命令简介" class="headerlink" title="命令简介"></a>命令简介</h1><p>周期性定时任务</p><h1 id="crontab语法"><a href="#crontab语法" class="headerlink" title="crontab语法"></a>crontab语法</h1><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">*   #每（分时日月周）执行</span><br><span class="line">[a-b] #在a到b的时间段执行</span><br><span class="line">*/n #每n(分时日月周)执行一次</span><br><span class="line">[a,b,c] #第(分时日月周)执行</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h1 id="案例"><a href="#案例" class="headerlink" title="案例"></a>案例</h1><p>只要收录了一些时间用法，具体的执行的内容都用A代替</p><ul><li>每一分钟执行一次<figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">*****A</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>在 12 月内, 每天的早上 6 点到 12 点，每隔 3 个小时 0 分钟执行一次</p><figure class="highlight apache"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attribute">0</span><span class="number">6</span>-<span class="number">12</span>/<span class="number">3</span>*<span class="number">12</span>*A</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>周一到周五每天下午 5:00 执行</p><figure class="highlight apache"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attribute">0</span><span class="number">17</span>**<span class="number">1</span>-<span class="number">5</span>A</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li>每月每天的午夜 0 点 20 分, 2 点 20 分, 4 点 20 分….执行<figure class="highlight apache"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attribute">20</span><span class="number">0</span>-<span class="number">24</span>/<span class="number">2</span>***A</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li>每两个小时执行<figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="bullet">*</span><span class="emphasis">*/2*</span>**  A</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li>每天7：50执行<figure class="highlight apache"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attribute">50</span><span class="number">7</span>***A</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li>每天22：50执行<figure class="highlight apache"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attribute">50</span><span class="number">22</span>***A</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li>每月1号和15号执行<figure class="highlight apache"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attribute">0</span><span class="number">0</span><span class="number">1</span>,<span class="number">15</span>**A</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li>每小时的第一分执行<figure class="highlight css"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="number">1</span>**** <span class="selector-tag">A</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li>每月的1、11、21、31日是的6：30执行<figure class="highlight apache"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attribute">30</span><span class="number">6</span>*/<span class="number">10</span>**A</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ul>]]></content>
    
    
    <summary type="html">在centos上使用定时任务实现24小时&quot;全勤无休&quot;</summary>
    
    
    
